modName: No Dragon Priest encounters for WiS
summary: You no more fight with generic dragon priests. Fix for Wars in Skyrim.
descriptionHtml:
You no more fight with generic dragon priests. Fix for Wars in Skyrim, so you need this mod first.

Link to wars in skyrim: http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=6176

This mod should work with all versions of Wars in Skyrim, and is tecnically a stand-alone from it.

I suggest you my other mod: this one change the difficult of Wars in Skyrim, for more easier fights!

http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=12901 

This version is more easier than rainbow mode, and contains the dragon priests fix, so delete this one before installing it.
author: Alfx3
